---
description: "How to proceed after a validation (jsonlint) or test failure: stop and report"
type: agent-select
alwaysApply: false
---
- On initial validation (for example `jsonlint`) or test failures, stop further edits.
- This rule applies to first-attempt failures only. After 3 failed attempts, the problem-solving rule (see `problem-solving.mdc`) takes precedence.
- Output the failure reason and suggested next steps.
